      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ANTIQUE STAR (1) sat handy and put her rivals to the sword, winning by 2.5L over the 2200m journey last time out. This shapes similarly today and she showed last start she has enough early speed to get across from the draw. Only rises 0.5kg for that effort and can go back-to-back. SAVORSKI (7) finished behind ANTIQUE STAR last time out and gets a few things in his favour today with an inside alley. Best form stacks right up and he should get every chance. DARK LOOKS (3) is not to be discounted after sticking on for third from the back half of the field last start. Can close off strongly from near the tail of the field. I LOVE YOUR SMILE (2) was solid late first-up over the mile and jumps straight to 2100m second-up. She does improve sharply into her campaign though and she's not to be discounted on the quick turnaround. CANDLELIGHT SUPPER (4) can improve third-up and out in distance.",
